<pc>，</pc>兀朮入侵<pc>，</pc>浚召<name key="王彥" type="givenName">彥</name>與吳玠<pc>、</pc>劉子羽會於興元<pc>。</pc>撒離曷自上津疾馳<pc>，</pc>不<measure quantity="1" unit="day">
